com.kontakt.sdk.android.manager

Interface ActionManager.ActionNotifier

  • Enclosing class:
    ActionManager

    public static interface ActionManager.ActionNotifier
    Action notifier is part of Action Management configuration. Once the actions list are found for certain proximity, the onActionsFound method is called. Please, note that when you enable Actions interaction using Action Manager (ActionManager) the methods of notifier will be invoked in thread different than UI Thread.

    • Field Summary
